Phobia hid inside his ship, it was an insignificant target compared 
to the cave.

"This is getting rediculous" he said as he spliced a few more wires 
together. "Diagnostics report on the weapons and shields.

"The ship glowed back to life, "Shields back to 80 percent, weapons 
online."

"Good" Phobia replied "Target attacking Maximals, 10 percent 
firepower, fire when ready."

The ship raised up into the air to get a clear shot and fired.

OOC last time the ship fired at 10 percent it barely charred the 
ground. so I don't want any complaining about it's use.
